Komatsu is to showcase its solutions at CONEXPO-CON/AGG 2020 in Las Vegas, Nevada, US. Komatsu is an industry-leading manufacturer and supplier of equipment, technologies and services for the construction, forklift, forestry, mining and industrial markets. Companies worldwide rely on our equipment, technology, services and solutions to develop infrastructure, extract minerals, maintain natural resources and create consumer products. Please visit booth N10825 at the 2020 CONEXPO show to learn more about how Smart Construction and KOMTRAX can help you harness the power of data, sensors and GPS technology to get your work done and see all the newest products for construction, quarry, forestry and more.